    "description": "<p>GAIN CITY BEST-ELECTRIC PTE LTD</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Looking for a challenging and rewarding career in a fast paced organization? Join Gain City!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nEstablished in 1981, Gain City is one of Singapore‘s leading retail brand carrying a wide range of quality air-conditioners, home appliances, audio visual equipment, digital and IT products. It is a multi-faceted organisation with distinctive track records in retail and wholesales operations, manufacturing, maintenance and repair, commercial, industrial and residential projects, import and export.<br />\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gain City the leading home-grown appliances and electronic retail store is also proud to be the recipient of the prestigious Enterprise 50 Award (5 times), Singapore Prestige Brand Award 2011 (Winner, SPBA-Heritage Brand). Gain City has also previously awarded other celebrated award such as the ISO 9001-2000 Certification, Super Brand (2004,2005,2006,2008 & 2009) and Singapore Promising Brand Award (2006).<br />\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n",
